{"tid":1812371,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【港詭實錄】港產恐怖遊戲融合本地都市傳說　超熟悉場景非常心寒","createTime":"2020-01-05T12:25:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T08:51:33.000Z","uid":85180,"like":7,"dislike":109,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"3e00ccf3d20d3f79e95d8ee071fa95f80652b8fc","tid":1812371,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T12:25:10.000Z","msg":"【港詭實錄】港產恐怖遊戲融合本地都市傳說 超熟悉場景非常心寒<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e0f256623ab170deb421bc1.jpg/mN0-BNZt3GQRznweC2KTaKnDFWbpqYuS6-1zbevtc20?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e0f256623ab170deb421bc1.jpg%2FmN0-BNZt3GQRznweC2KTaKnDFWbpqYuS6-1zbevtc20%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=5a2dfc75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n撰文：gamebase<br />\n2020-01-05 11:00<br />\n最後更新日期：2020-01-05 11:00<br />\n遊戲發行商 Gamera Game 近日宣布，由香港的獨立遊戲工作室 Ghostpie Studio 所開發的第一人稱恐怖遊戲《港詭實錄》將在 1 月 6 日正式在 Steam 上推出。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e0edf2323ab170deb4218fe.jpg/MmIUYWQ4ybQZThoKI6ABjeYoa0iwF16pmOYJKJjmCSg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e0edf2323ab170deb4218fe.jpg%2FMmIUYWQ4ybQZThoKI6ABjeYoa0iwF16pmOYJKJjmCSg&h=ab9f77a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e0edf23b66f770df1c1d410.jpg/fmglfd4JvRlrfid8FPvW-Ki_Bo6ajH7x5HSKRuR0ikY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e0edf23b66f770df1c1d410.jpg%2Ffmglfd4JvRlrfid8FPvW-Ki_Bo6ajH7x5HSKRuR0ikY&h=24a2f2fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e0edf23fd5cc31c9c2b8a72.jpg/l_0wxH8IMCL_-SAp9uqXRDuZSkCUUiSu0Ewd1tBMHdY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e0edf23fd5cc31c9c2b8a72.jpg%2Fl_0wxH8IMCL_-SAp9uqXRDuZSkCUUiSu0Ewd1tBMHdY&h=7794df81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e0edf23b66f770df1c1d412.jpg/f6Uo-DLyaQe2_WyLQW05MH-Rdz_ECSVTdT-bUnU_m1I\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e0edf23b66f770df1c1d412.jpg%2Ff6Uo-DLyaQe2_WyLQW05MH-Rdz_ECSVTdT-bUnU_m1I&h=e79385d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e0edf2323ab170deb421900.jpg/9Ar778WfLg9J7DmkgVMRjlGIk98pjsEzj6K9m4-ivZs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e0edf2323ab170deb421900.jpg%2F9Ar778WfLg9J7DmkgVMRjlGIk98pjsEzj6K9m4-ivZs&h=78f3d351&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e0edf23b66f770df1c1d413.jpg/OgJPOdexxa9uCNHpKwIjZ3wnqkSlIBynVdXr4lXV6-I\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e0edf23b66f770df1c1d413.jpg%2FOgJPOdexxa9uCNHpKwIjZ3wnqkSlIBynVdXr4lXV6-I&h=d3c8d2c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e0edf2313d12b1ca2b90819.jpg/ZsrSPh2FbDt3Q5Viu3U2a0IalmlX64aGCY_c9gmP3PY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e0edf2313d12b1ca2b90819.jpg%2FZsrSPh2FbDt3Q5Viu3U2a0IalmlX64aGCY_c9gmP3PY&h=5bc7bcac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《港詭實錄》（原名《牛一》）是一款以香港都市傳說為題材的第一人稱恐怖冒險遊戲。故事講述一群年輕人為了錄製靈異節目「逃出靈界點」來到九龍城寨遺址，然而這次的錄製卻因為一些突發事件變得詭異起來。節目組員陸續失蹤、女主持人嘉慧的行為變得十分古怪，深陷其中的男主角阿樂開始懷疑是否觸碰到了某些禁忌，面對一連串的恐怖與謎團，他滿腦子想的就是趕快找到嘉慧立刻逃出這裡。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲融合大量香港本地的都市傳說，能夠從中體驗到許多獨特的本地文化與民俗習慣，此外遊戲還原了唐樓、粵劇戲棚、港式屋邨等極具中國地方文化特色的建築，玩家可以在其中自由探索，感受濃厚的香港氛圍。玩家需要在九龍城寨遺址中尋找解開謎團的線索，努力還原整個世界的真相，途中將會出現恐怖的敵人，要一邊躲避它們的追擊並找出逃離的道路。對香港的都市傳說感興趣或喜愛恐怖遊戲的玩家不妨在遊戲正式推出後來感受獨特恐怖氣氛的《港詭實錄》吧。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=37&amp;v=lUGpivp94IQ&amp;feature=emb_logo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D37%26v%3DlUGpivp94IQ%26feature%3Demb_logo&d=4MF4O%2Bfy8eJNXT4C%2FvKi1ZmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=324a5544\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=37&amp;v=lUGpivp94IQ&amp;feature=emb_logo</a>"},{"pid":"85a5e0455372240de9ff505a8c7712d043547797","tid":1812371,"uid":85180,"like":65,"dislike":2,"score":63,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T12:26:56.000Z","msg":"奶共game"},{"pid":"129054a131982f95b64561c9662deb69611930da","tid":1812371,"uid":92951,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T12:28:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />s<br />\n早兩日睇<br />\nsteam到寫中國香港喎"},{"pid":"a5451e981f8bd7aa1513e549fab7d3e6e4de7c55","tid":1812371,"uid":46587,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T12:28:18.000Z","msg":"見到返校、還願做起左就食佢條水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cdab20235e2220370f1161829f97b1ffa2916da","tid":1812371,"uid":126649,"like":93,"dislike":4,"score":89,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T12:31:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yKR1RMN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyKR1RMN.png&h=a1d1ec7e&s={SIZE}\" /> 不了"},{"pid":"383779000edea64eef63a7ab2286759875439052","tid":1812371,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T12:31:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f810535d55bbd3be82a32165aa579d3dff21473","tid":1812371,"uid":214502,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T12:32:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://keylol.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=550090\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkeylol.com%2Fforum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D550090&d=4MF4O%2Bfy8eJNXT4C%2FvKi1ZmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=ad1a1efa\" target=\"_blank\">https://keylol.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=550090</a><br />\n由<strong>中國香港</strong>的GHOSTPIE遊戲工作室開發，Gamera Game代理發行的生存恐怖遊戲《港詭實錄》，將於1月6日正式在Steam上發售，